{
  "stem": "14060.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The secular dates we knew, because anybody, even a guard or a-- there was, for instance, in that factory, there were hundreds and hundreds of forced labor workers.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was the Organisation Todt that was a labor organization who were elderly Germans, similar to the Wehrmacht, but doing work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- or supervising work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some of them were quite reasonable people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They didn't hit us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or didn't-- it happened, but not on a regular basis.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you could ask them what date it is today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, they-- they-- it depends who you were or what you were doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If you helped him up-- just that he dropped the pan-- you could ask him, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But people knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, there-- there-- in every camp there was an office which was dated, events recorded, so there was not a problem.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Jews can work out if [HEBREW] is on Saturday on this date, then Tisha B'av is three weeks later, and therefore Rosh Hashana is on that date.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was not a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I must tell you in the early part of our existence there, there was quite a lot of bombing by the Americans, daytime bombing, because it was an important industrial complex there.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the practice was that all the Germans and the forced laborers and the non-Jews were allowed to go out of the factory into bunkers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The Jews, not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Jews were led out of the-- of the factory perimeter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were sent down into an sandgrube, which is a sand pit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The sand pit consisted of a road approximately three, four, meters wide on the bottom, and then a sand bank going up on both sides, I would say, at least three or four stories high.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
